snippet.title: Kingdom Hearts 0.2 Birth by Sleep: A Fragmentary Passage Full Gameplay (1080p 60fps - Proud Mode)
snippet.description:
Kingdom Hearts 0.2 Birth by Sleep: A Fragmentary Passage (Proud - No Commentary) - KH HD 2.8 Final Chapter Prologue

2:16 Kingdom Hearts 0.2 Birth by Sleep - Opening Theme
5:15 New Game (Proud Mode)


WORLDS (Realm of Darkness)
8:16 Dark World (Castle of Dreams)
32:18 The World Within (Dwarf Woodlands)
1:02:28 Forest of Thorns (Enchanted Dominion)
1:30:50 Depths of Darkness - Final World (Destiny Islands)

BOSS FIGHTS
27:00 Demon Tower (1st phase)
38:44 Phantom Aqua (1st phase)
51:18 Phantom Aqua (2nd phase)
54:36 Phantom Aqua (3rd phase & Final)
1:07:27 Darkside (1st phase)
1:22:00 Darkside (2nd phase + Army)
1:31:21 Demon Tower (2nd phase)
1:50:28 Demon Tide - Final Boss & Ending

PLAYSTATION TROPHIES & ACHIEVEMENTS
13:33 Wandering in the Dark (Bronze Trophy)
27:27 A Magical Finale (Bronze Trophy)
32:18 Flow of Time (Bronze Trophy)
42:36 Shotlock Star (Bronze Trophy)
44:20 Dark Explorer (Bronze Trophy)
1:02:16 False Temptations (Bronze Trophy)
1:12:26 Ice Queen (Bronze Trophy)
1:26:20 Real or Illusion? (Bronze Trophy)
1:40:32 Fashionista (Bronze Trophy)
2:21:53 Into the Depths of Darkness (Bronze Trophy) & Proud Player/Critical Competitor (Silver Trophy)

SONGS USED

Opening:(INSTRUMENTAL GarageBand Remake) Kingdom Hearts 0.2 BBS - "Simple and Clean -Ray of Hope MIX-" by SilverTom93 https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bmBwUmgFot4

Ending: Kingdom Hearts - Simple and Clean (Remix) by Sylvia Tse https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0l0cUXKKghM
